              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-center mb-4">Sanación emocional</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-body-500">
              Procesos para integrar emociones difíciles, transformar patrones limitantes y sanar heridas del pasado.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-medium text-center mb-4">Energía renovada</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-body-500">
              Recupera vitalidad al liberar el desgaste que producen los pensamientos rumiativos y las preocupaciones constantes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 transform transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
              </svg>
